<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mnṣwr ạnạ byk wgẖạlb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - mnṣwr ạnạ byk wgẖạlb wạlṣʿb byk hʿdy̱
 wyqyn mn jwh qlby̱ ksbạn by̱k ạltḥdy̱
 1- bryẗ wmrh jdạaⁿ wmtạhẗ ṣʿbẗ fʿlạaⁿ wjfạf wạlạrḍ nạsẖfẗ
 ( lkn hạʿbrhạ ḥtmạaⁿ )2
 ymkn fyhạ ạlạ̉m wmsẖạkl btqblny̱ lkn hạqdr ʿlyhạ
 ( ạṣl ạnt ạlly̱ ḍạmny̱ )2
 2- ạlʿyn tsẖwf sẖkwk wtqwl ạmly̱ bʿyd
 bs fy̱ qlby̱ jsạrẗ ( whnạdy ạlmwạʿyd)2
 mʿ kl ywm yfwt bạkbr wạfhm ktyr
 wyzyd fy̱ ạlqlb sẖwq ( ytḥdy̱ ạlmstḥyl )2</lyrics>
<author>sạmḥ ʿbdh, bhyr ạ̹dwạrd</author>
